title: Nirvana Live Bootleg Collection
description:
This is my first time trying to upload a torrent and i'm technologically retarded, so bare with me.

I've had these bootlegs sitting around for 20+ years and I thought it was time to get them out there. The audio quality varies, but all are very listenable. The tracklists are as follows:
